---
import '@/styles/theme.css';
import '@/styles/global.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
    <title>見た目調整 | 風呂は命の洗濯</title>
  </head>
  <body class="lab-page">
    <main class="lab-shell">
      <header class="lab-header">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Style Lab</p>
          <h1>見た目調整</h1>
          <p>本番ブログに近いプレビューを見ながら、幅・余白・文字・色を細かく試せます。</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/">ブログへ戻る</a>
      </header>

      <section class="workspace" aria-label="見た目調整ワークスペース">
        <aside class="panel" aria-label="調整パネル">
          <div class="panel-block">
            <h2>幅と余白</h2>
            <label>
              <span>ページ全体</span>
              <input data-key="page" type="range" min="1080" max="1520" step="10" />
              <output data-value="page"></output>
            </label>
            <label>
              <span>本文</span>
              <input data-key="main" type="range" min="720" max="1080" step="10" />
              <output data-value="main"></output>
            </label>
            <label>
              <span>Profile欄</span>
              <input data-key="sidebar" type="range" min="200" max="320" step="10" />
              <output data-value="sidebar"></output>
            </label>
            <label>
              <span>本文とProfileの間</span>
              <input data-key="gap" type="range" min="24" max="120" step="4" />
              <output data-value="gap"></output>
            </label>
            <label>
              <span>外側の余白</span>
              <input data-key="sidePadding" type="range" min="0" max="56" step="2" />
              <output data-value="sidePadding"></output>
            </label>
            <label>
              <span>Profileの下げ幅</span>
              <input data-key="offset" type="range" min="0" max="80" step="2" />
              <output data-value="offset"></output>
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="panel-block">
            <h2>文字</h2>
            <label>
              <span>本文サイズ</span>
              <input data-key="font" type="range" min="15" max="20" step="0.5" />
              <output data-value="font"></output>
            </label>
            <label>
              <span>行間</span>
              <input data-key="lineHeight" type="range" min="1.55" max="2.15" step="0.05" />
              <output data-value="lineHeight"></output>
            </label>
            <label>
              <span>タイトルサイズ</span>
              <input data-key="titleSize" type="range" min="30" max="58" step="1" />
              <output data-value="titleSize"></output>
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="panel-block color-grid">
            <h2>色</h2>
            <label>
              <span>背景</span>
              <input data-key="background" type="color" />
            </label>
            <label>
              <span>文字</span>
              <input data-key="text" type="color" />
            </label>
            <label>
              <span>アクセント</span>
              <input data-key="link" type="color" />
            </label>
            <label>
              <span>薄い文字</span>
              <input data-key="muted" type="color" />
            </label>
            <label>
              <span>線</span>
              <input data-key="border" type="color" />
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="panel-block">
            <h2>形</h2>
            <div class="button-row">
              <button type="button" data-preset="wide">本文広め</button>
              <button type="button" data-preset="calm">落ち着き</button>
              <button type="button" data-preset="compact">余白少なめ</button>
            </div>
            <button type="button" class="ghost-button" id="resetButton">最初に戻す</button>
          </div>
        </aside>

        <section class="preview-section" aria-label="プレビュー">
          <div class="preview-topbar">
            <div>
              <strong>プレビュー</strong>
              <span>紫のつまみをドラッグできます</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metrics">
              <span>本文 <output data-value="main"></output></span>
              <span>Profile <output data-value="sidebar"></output></span>
              <span>間 <output data-value="gap"></output></span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="preview-canvas" id="previewCanvas">
            <div class="mock-page" id="mockPage">
              <header class="mock-site-header">
                <a class="mock-title" href="#">風呂は命の洗濯</a>
                <p>Literature, Phenomenology &amp; Criticism</p>
                <nav>
                  <a href="#">Home</a>
                  <a href="#">Archive</a>
                  <a href="#">Categories</a>
                  <a href="#">About</a>
                  <a href="#">RSS</a>
                </nav>
              </header>

              <main class="mock-grid">
                <article class="mock-main">
                  <h1>読書メモの表示サンプル</h1>
                  <p class="mock-meta">2026年5月31日 / 読書メモ</p>
                  <p>
                    ここが記事本文です。日本語の長文を読んだときに、横幅が広すぎないか、狭すぎないかを確認できます。
                    本文の幅、行間、サイドバーとの距離が合うと、読むときの圧迫感がかなり減ります。
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    右の Profile 欄を脇に逃がしたいときは、本文幅を広げつつ、Profile 欄を少し細くし、間隔を広げるのが効きます。
                    外側の余白は、ページ全体が画面の端へどれくらい近づくかを決めます。
                  </p>
                  <h2>小見出し</h2>
                  <p>
                    見出し、本文、引用、表の雰囲気を同時に見られるようにしています。
                    気に入った値ができたら、下の「反映用の値」をそのまま送ってください。
                  </p>
                  <blockquote>引用や補足が入ったときの見え方も、この幅で確認できます。</blockquote>
                </article>

                <div class="divider-handle" id="dividerHandle" role="separator" aria-label="本文とProfile欄の境目を調整">
                  <span>境目</span>
                </div>

                <aside class="mock-sidebar">
                  <section>
                    <h2>Profile</h2>
                    <p><strong>さもの</strong></p>
                    <p>文学・哲学・批評理論についての読書メモと短い試論。</p>
                  </section>
                  <section>
                    <h2>Recent Entries</h2>
                    <p>このブログについて</p>
                    <p>読書メモの表示サンプル</p>
                  </section>
                  <section>
                    <h2>Categories</h2>
                    <p>読書メモ (1)</p>
                    <p>雑記 (1)</p>
                  </section>
                </aside>
              </main>

              <div class="page-handle" id="pageHandle" role="separator" aria-label="ページ全体の幅を調整">
                <span>全体幅</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <section class="readout" aria-label="反映用の値">
            <div>
              <h2>反映用の値</h2>
              <p>気に入ったら、この内容をそのまま送ってください。</p>
            </div>
            <textarea id="cssOutput" readonly></textarea>
            <button type="button" id="copyButton">コピー</button>
          </section>
        </section>
      </section>
    </main>

    <script>
      // @ts-nocheck
      const initial = {
        page: 1340,
        main: 940,
        sidebar: 240,
        gap: 64,
        sidePadding: 12,
        offset: 18,
        font: 17,
        lineHeight: 1.9,
        titleSize: 40,
        background: '#fdfcf9',
        text: '#1f1f1f',
        muted: '#6b6760',
        link: '#5a4a78',
        border: '#dedbd4',
      };
      const state = { ...initial };
      const ranges = document.querySelectorAll('input[data-key]');
      const outputs = document.querySelectorAll('output[data-value]');
      const cssOutput = document.querySelector('#cssOutput');
      const copyButton = document.querySelector('#copyButton');
      const resetButton = document.querySelector('#resetButton');
      const dividerHandle = document.querySelector('#dividerHandle');
      const pageHandle = document.querySelector('#pageHandle');

      function clamp(value, min, max) {
        return Math.max(min, Math.min(max, value));
      }

      function darken(hex) {
        const color = hex.replace('#', '');
        const parts = [0, 2, 4].map((start) => parseInt(color.slice(start, start + 2), 16));
        return `#${parts.map((part) => clamp(part - 30, 0, 255).toString(16).padStart(2, '0')).join('')}`;
      }

      function syncInputs() {
        ranges.forEach((input) => {
          input.value = state[input.dataset.key];
        });
      }

      function syncOutputs() {
        outputs.forEach((output) => {
          const value = state[output.dataset.value];
          output.textContent = typeof value === 'number' ? `${value}px` : value;
          if (output.dataset.value === 'lineHeight') output.textContent = value;
        });
      }

      function applyState() {
        const root = document.documentElement;
        root.style.setProperty('--lab-page-width', `${state.page}px`);
        root.style.setProperty('--lab-main-width', `${state.main}px`);
        root.style.setProperty('--lab-sidebar-width', `${state.sidebar}px`);
        root.style.setProperty('--lab-gap', `${state.gap}px`);
        root.style.setProperty('--lab-side-padding', `${state.sidePadding}px`);
        root.style.setProperty('--lab-offset', `${state.offset}px`);
        root.style.setProperty('--blog-font-size', `${state.font}px`);
        root.style.setProperty('--blog-line-height', state.lineHeight);
        root.style.setProperty('--lab-title-size', `${state.titleSize}px`);
        root.style.setProperty('--blog-background', state.background);
        root.style.setProperty('--blog-text', state.text);
        root.style.setProperty('--blog-muted-text', state.muted);
        root.style.setProperty('--blog-link', state.link);
        root.style.setProperty('--blog-link-hover', darken(state.link));
        root.style.setProperty('--blog-border', state.border);
        syncInputs();
        syncOutputs();
        cssOutput.value = [
          `--blog-background: ${state.background};`,
          `--blog-text: ${state.text};`,
          `--blog-muted-text: ${state.muted};`,
          `--blog-link: ${state.link};`,
          `--blog-link-hover: ${darken(state.link)};`,
          `--blog-border: ${state.border};`,
          `--blog-font-size: ${state.font}px;`,
          `--blog-line-height: ${state.lineHeight};`,
          `--blog-page-width: ${state.page}px;`,
          `--blog-main-width: ${state.main}px;`,
          `--blog-sidebar-width: ${state.sidebar}px;`,
          `--blog-column-gap: ${state.gap}px;`,
          `--blog-sidebar-offset: ${state.offset}px;`,
          `--blog-side-padding: ${state.sidePadding}px;`,
        ].join('\n');
      }

      function updateFromInput(input) {
        const key = input.dataset.key;
        state[key] = input.type === 'color' ? input.value : Number(input.value);
        applyState();
      }

      function setPreset(name) {
        if (name === 'wide') {
          Object.assign(state, { page: 1420, main: 1020, sidebar: 220, gap: 76, sidePadding: 8 });
        }
        if (name === 'calm') {
          Object.assign(state, { page: 1240, main: 820, sidebar: 260, gap: 64, sidePadding: 28, font: 17, lineHeight: 1.9 });
        }
        if (name === 'compact') {
          Object.assign(state, { page: 1320, main: 940, sidebar: 230, gap: 48, sidePadding: 6 });
        }
        applyState();
      }

      function startDividerDrag(event) {
        event.preventDefault();
        const startX = event.clientX;
        const startMain = state.main;
        const startSidebar = state.sidebar;
        function move(moveEvent) {
          const delta = moveEvent.clientX - startX;
          state.main = clamp(Math.round(startMain + delta), 720, 1080);
          state.sidebar = clamp(Math.round(startSidebar - delta), 200, 320);
          state.page = state.main + state.sidebar + state.gap + 52;
          applyState();
        }
        attachDrag(move);
      }

      function startPageDrag(event) {
        event.preventDefault();
        const startX = event.clientX;
        const startPage = state.page;
        function move(moveEvent) {
          const delta = moveEvent.clientX - startX;
          state.page = clamp(Math.round(startPage + delta), 1080, 1520);
          applyState();
        }
        attachDrag(move);
      }

      function attachDrag(move) {
        function up() {
          window.removeEventListener('pointermove', move);
          window.removeEventListener('pointerup', up);
        }
        window.addEventListener('pointermove', move);
        window.addEventListener('pointerup', up);
      }

      ranges.forEach((input) => input.addEventListener('input', () => updateFromInput(input)));
      document.querySelectorAll('[data-preset]').forEach((button) => {
        button.addEventListener('click', () => setPreset(button.dataset.preset));
      });
      resetButton.addEventListener('click', () => {
        Object.assign(state, initial);
        applyState();
      });
      dividerHandle.addEventListener('pointerdown', startDividerDrag);
      pageHandle.addEventListener('pointerdown', startPageDrag);
      copyButton.addEventListener('click', async () => {
        await navigator.clipboard.writeText(cssOutput.value);
        copyButton.textContent = 'コピーしました';
        setTimeout(() => {
          copyButton.textContent = 'コピー';
        }, 1200);
      });

      applyState();
    </script>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .lab-page {
    background: var(--blog-background);
  }

  .lab-shell {
    width: min(1500px, calc(100% - 24px));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1.2rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .lab-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--blog-border);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--blog-link);
    font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0.1rem 0 0.35rem;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }

  .lab-header p:last-child {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--blog-muted-text);
  }

  .workspace {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 320px minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .panel,
  .preview-section,
  .readout {
    border: 1px solid var(--blog-border);
    background: var(--blog-surface);
  }

  .panel {
    position: sticky;
    top: 12px;
    max-height: calc(100vh - 24px);
    overflow: auto;
    padding: 1rem;
    font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .panel-block + .panel-block {
    margin-top: 1.2rem;
    padding-top: 1.2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--blog-border);
  }

  .panel h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  label {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 0.35rem 0.65rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  label input[type='range'] {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    width: 100%;
  }

  input[type='color'] {
    width: 74px;
    height: 34px;
    border: 1px solid var(--blog-border);
    background: var(--blog-surface);
  }

  output {
    min-width: 54px;
    color: var(--blog-link);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .color-grid label {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
  }

  .button-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .button-row button:first-child {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
  }

  button {
    border: 1px solid var(--blog-link);
    padding: 0.6rem 0.75rem;
    background: var(--blog-link);
    color: white;
    font: inherit;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ghost-button {
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 0.6rem;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--blog-link);
  }

  .preview-section {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .preview-topbar {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--blog-border);
    font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .preview-topbar span {
    color: var(--blog-muted-text);
  }

  .metrics {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .preview-canvas {
    overflow: auto;
    padding: 26px;
    background:
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(90, 74, 120, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(90, 74, 120, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 24px 24px;
  }

  .mock-page {
    --lab-page-width: 1340px;
    --lab-main-width: 940px;
    --lab-sidebar-width: 240px;
    --lab-gap: 64px;
    --lab-side-padding: 12px;
    --lab-offset: 18px;
    --lab-title-size: 40px;
    position: relative;
    width: var(--lab-page-width);
    min-width: 980px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--lab-side-padding) 28px;
    border: 2px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--blog-link) 42%, var(--blog-border));
    background: var(--blog-background);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(31, 31, 31, 0.09);
  }

  .mock-site-header {
    padding: 28px 0 18px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--blog-border);
  }

  .mock-title {
    display: block;
    color: var(--blog-text);
    font-size: var(--lab-title-size);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .mock-site-header p {
    margin: 0.35rem 0 1rem;
    color: var(--blog-muted-text);
    font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .mock-site-header nav {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4rem 1.1rem;
    font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .mock-grid {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: var(--lab-main-width) var(--lab-sidebar-width);
    gap: var(--lab-gap);
    align-items: start;
    padding-top: 2.2rem;
  }

  .mock-main h1 {
    margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .mock-main h2 {
    margin: 2rem 0 0.8rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.25rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--blog-border);
    font-size: 1.45rem;
  }

  .mock-main p {
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .mock-meta {
    color: var(--blog-muted-text);
    font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .mock-sidebar {
    margin-top: var(--lab-offset);
    color: var(--blog-muted-text);
    font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .mock-sidebar section {
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--blog-border);
  }

  .mock-sidebar h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.45rem;
    color: var(--blog-text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .mock-sidebar p {
    margin: 0.25rem 0;
  }

  .divider-handle,
  .page-handle {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 2;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--blog-link) 52%, var(--blog-border));
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--blog-link) 20%, var(--blog-surface));
    color: var(--blog-link);
    cursor: ew-resize;
    touch-action: none;
    font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .divider-handle {
    top: 40px;
    bottom: 22px;
    left: calc(var(--lab-main-width) + (var(--lab-gap) / 2) - 13px);
    width: 26px;
  }

  .divider-handle span,
  .page-handle span {
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
  }

  .page-handle {
    top: 50%;
    right: -13px;
    width: 26px;
    height: 190px;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
  }

  .readout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr 110px;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
  }

  .readout h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .readout p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--blog-muted-text);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
  }

  textarea {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 130px;
    resize: vertical;
    border: 1px solid var(--blog-border);
    padding: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--blog-background);
    color: var(--blog-text);
    font: 0.82rem/1.6 ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .workspace {
      display: block;
    }

    .panel {
      position: static;
      max-height: none;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .readout {
      display: block;
    }

    textarea,
    .readout button {
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
    }

    .readout button {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
